<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>. . . ]Ammianos [ . .c. 42 . . and no-one else shall have ] a right [ to bury here . . . c. 35 . . . since whoever] undertakes [ to do so shall pay . . .? . . . of which one third] shall be [for the prosecutor; and none the less shall my instructions remain valid. A copy of the] inscription [was deposited in the Property -archive in the stephanephorate] of Flavius (or Flavia) Deme[trios (or Demetria) month ?]</p>
</div>
